  "text": "[ ![weather25.com](https://www.weather25.com/images/weather25-black.svg) ](https://www.weather25.com \"weather25.com\")\n[United States](https://www.weather25.com/north-america/usa \"Weather in United States\") [England](https://www.weather25.com/europe/united-kingdom \"Weather in England\") [Australia](https://www.weather25.com/oceania/australia \"Weather in Australia\") [Canada](https://www.weather25.com/north-america/canada \"Weather in Canada\")\n°F °C\n![Search](https://res.weather25.com/images/icons/search_white_new.svg)\nTokyo ![weather in Japan](https://res.weather25.com/images/r-flags/japan.svg)\nWeather in May 2026 \n  * [ Overview ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo)\n  * [ 14 Days ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=14)\n  * [ May ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=May)\n  * [ June ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=June)\n  * [ Long range ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=long-range)\n  * [ Today ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=today)\n  * [ Tomorrow ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=tomorrow)\n\n\n![Remove from your favorite locations](https://res.weather25.com/images/icons/filled-star.svg) ![Add to my locations](https://res.weather25.com/images/icons/empty-star.svg)\n![Share](https://res.weather25.com/images/icons/share.svg)\n  1. [ Home](https://www.weather25.com)\n  2. [Asia](https://www.weather25.com/asia)\n  3. [ ![weather in Japan](https://res.weather25.com/images/r-flags/japan.svg)Japan](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan)\n  4. [Tokyo](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo)\n  5. [May](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=May)\n\n\nLocation was added to [My Locations](https://www.weather25.com/my-locations)\nLocation was removed from [My Locations](https://www.weather25.com/my-locations)\n[ April ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=April)\nAomori Asahikawa Beppu Chiba Fuji Fujikawaguchiko Fukuoka Funabashi Furano Hakodate Hakone Hakuba Hamamatsu Hiroshima Kagoshima Kamakura Kanazawa Karuizawa Kawaguchi Kawasaki Kitakyushu Kobe Kumamoto Kushiro Kyoto Matsumoto Nagano Nagasaki Nagoya Nara Niigata Nikko Niseko Noboribetsu Okayama Okinawa Osaka Otaru Sakai Sapporo Sasebo Sendai Shirakawa Takayama Tokyo Yokohama Yuzawa\n[ June ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=June)\n# Tokyo weather in May 2026\nClick on a day for an hourly weather forecast\n[ Friday May 29 0.3 mm 28° / 21° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=today)[ Saturday May 30 1.3 mm 27° / 20° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=tomorrow)[ Sunday May 31 0 mm 29° / 22° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-05-31)[ Monday Jun 1 0 mm 30° / 23° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-01)[ Tuesday Jun 2 0 mm 27° / 21° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-02)[ Wednesday Jun 3 2.5 mm 24° / 21° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-03)[ Thursday Jun 4 105.8 mm 21° / 17° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-04)[ Friday Jun 5 0 mm 20° / 17° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-05)[ Saturday Jun 6 0 mm 23° / 16° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-06)[ Sunday Jun 7 0 mm 25° / 18° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-07)[ Monday Jun 8 1.3 mm 24° / 20° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-08)[ Tuesday Jun 9 11.5 mm 24° / 20° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-09)[ Wednesday Jun 10 1.5 mm 27° / 22° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-10)[ Thursday Jun 11 0 mm 28° / 22° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=day#date=2026-06-11) [ Next  \nMonth >> ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=long-range)\n## The average weather in Tokyo in May\nThe **temperatures in Tokyo in May are comfortable** with low of 16°C and and high up to 23°C.\nYou can expect rain for roughly half of the month of May in Tokyo. We’re expecting roughly **8 to 15 days of rain** , so your rubber boots and umbrella are going to see plenty of use this month if you’re keen on staying dry.\nOur weather forecast can give you a great sense of what weather to expect in **Tokyo in May 2026**.\nIf you’re planning to visit Tokyo in the near future, we highly recommend that you review the [14 day weather forecast for Tokyo](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=14) before you arrive.\nTemperatures\n23° / 16° \nRainy Days\n8\nSnowy Days\n0\nDry Days\n23\nRainfall\n190\nmm\nSun Hours\n9.7\nHrs\nHistoric average weather for May\n[ ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=April)\nMay\n[ ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=month&month=June)  \n| Sun  | Mon  | Tue  | Wed  | Thu  | Fri  | Sat  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n|   |   |   |   |   | [ 1 21° /14° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=1&month=5 \"Weather in 1 may 2026\")  | [ 2 21° /14° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=2&month=5 \"Weather in 2 may 2026\")  |  \n| [ 3 21° /14° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=3&month=5 \"Weather in 3 may 2026\")  | [ 4 23° /16° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=4&month=5 \"Weather in 4 may 2026\")  | [ 5 23° /17° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=5&month=5 \"Weather in 5 may 2026\")  | [ 6 22° /17° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=6&month=5 \"Weather in 6 may 2026\")  | [ 7 21° /14° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/tokyo?page=past-weather#day=7&month=5 \"Weather in 7 may 2026\")  | [ 8 20° /14° ](https://www.weather25.com/asia/japan/toky